P(ortable) V(irtual)env
==================

This is Portable conda virtualenv. Just 1. download, 2. unarchive, 3. activate and 4. GO!

* = PVenv works purely in userspace in the dir with RW access. =
* = PVenv is isolated into its directory only (in install time, not runtime). =
* = PVenv is mutiplatform. (Build on the shoulder of the TITANS - anaconda.com.) =

How to use
==========

Linux AMD64 (+ docker)
----------------------

Linux ARM64 (+ docker in ARM MacOS)
----------------------

Windows AMD64 (+ docker Win containers)
----------------------

Windows ARM64
-------------

MacOS AMD64
-----------

MacOS ARM64
-----------

